Sentece: The Cmax and AUC0-infinity values for (+)-(S)-ethotoin were significantly greater than those for (-)-(R)-ethotoin (ratio of mean AUC0-infinity values 0.88), but the elimination half-lives of the isomers were virtually identical [12.35 +/- 5.15 h for (-)-(R)-ethotoin; 12.28 +/- 5.34 h for (+)-(S)-ethotoin].
Title: Enantioselective pharmacokinetics of ethotoin in humans following single oral doses of the racemate.
